856
01:13:46,255 --> 01:13:47,506
Jake!

857
01:14:10,696 --> 01:14:11,780
Jake!

858
01:14:14,825 --> 01:14:15,909
Daddy!

859
01:14:17,995 --> 01:14:19,288
Help.

860
01:14:20,747 --> 01:14:23,041
Daddy! Help me!

861
01:14:25,002 --> 01:14:27,754
