865
01:15:27,606 --> 01:15:28,815
Jake?

866
01:15:33,195 --> 01:15:34,279
Jake?

867
01:16:39,845 --> 01:16:41,179
God, please. God.

868
01:16:41,221 --> 01:16:42,556
No, no, no.

869
01:17:12,419 --> 01:17:13,503
